title: Microsoft Office Professional Plus (x64) 2013 + Activator
description:
How TO INSTALL MS OFFICE 2013

1. LAUNCH "Set-up.exe" AND FOLLOW INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

2. APPLY ACTIVATOR FROM THE MAP "Activator" (Microsoft Toolkit)

3. ENJOY YOUR FREE COPY OF MS OFFICE 2013!

See ScreenShot for the office programs included in the installation.
